1
00:01:19,640 --> 00:01:21,080
This is simply crazy.

2
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:24,120
At the Lu family's business gathering,

3
00:01:24,160 --> 00:01:26,240
you actually hit someone in public.

4
00:01:26,600 --> 00:01:28,840
What will others think of the Lu family?

5
00:01:29,320 --> 00:01:31,980
Do you have any regard for the Lu family's rules?

6
00:01:32,240 --> 00:01:33,600
He is Lu Zhenye,

7
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:35,920
the founder of the Lu Group.

8
00:01:37,440 --> 00:01:39,800
Zhenye, don't be angry.

9
00:01:40,039 --> 00:01:41,640
Zhixia is young

10
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:42,840
and acted on impulse.

11
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,560
Don't be too hard on her.

12
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,000
It's just that

13
00:01:47,039 --> 00:01:48,560
Yuran was wronged,

14
00:01:49,240 --> 00:01:51,840
and our Jingxi lost face.

15
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:54,440
If word of this gets out...

16
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:58,440
This is Lu Jingheng's stepmother.

17
00:01:58,759 --> 00:02:01,960
It seems the original host suffered a lot at their hands.

18
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:05,400
Shen Zhixia.

19
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:09,800
Shen Zhixia.

20
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,600
They made me dance in public.

21
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:14,040
Do I not have any dignity?

22
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:16,520
Don't think marrying into the Lu family

23
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:18,450
makes you worthy of being a member.

24
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:21,480
How can you compare yourself to Jingxi?

25
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:22,480
Who does she think she is?

26
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:22,720
You...

27
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:24,120
Who told you to talk back?

28
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,240
Go back to your room.

29
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:28,079
I won't.

30
00:02:28,640 --> 00:02:31,600
Go back to your room.

31
00:02:40,440 --> 00:02:41,240
Fine.

32
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,160
Dad, have a seat.

33
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:54,040
Actually, what happened today

34
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:55,370
wasn't Zhixia's fault.

35
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:57,720
Yuran was making things difficult first.

36
00:02:57,720 --> 00:03:01,160
Moreover, Lu Jingxi wanted to transfer the luxury agency rights

37
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:02,200
to the Su family,

38
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:03,800
but I've already rejected it.

39
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:04,600
Jingheng.

40
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:07,530
I know you like to do everything yourself.

41
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:10,040
But Jingxi is your own brother.

42
00:03:10,040 --> 00:03:11,900
He is also a child of the Lu family.

43
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:15,040
Your father agreed to this luxury business.

44
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:16,440
Dad agreed?

45
00:03:17,600 --> 00:03:19,060
I have read that contract.

46
00:03:19,760 --> 00:03:22,240
Secretly using company resources to pave the way for the Su family,

47
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,640
did Dad agree to that too?

48
00:03:23,920 --> 00:03:27,040
Dad, I have sent the contract to your room.

49
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:29,130
Please review it yourself.

50
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,360
Zhenye.

51
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:35,860
I only know that Yuran does business with the Lu family.

52
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:38,890
I don't know why that child is being so unreasonable.

53
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:40,200
Zhenye.

54
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:44,600
You don't need to say anything about this.

55
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:47,860
Let Jingxi come and explain it to me herself.

56
00:03:53,200 --> 00:03:54,560
This Su Yuran.

57
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:57,640
Even if she isn't the one who killed the original owner,

58
00:03:57,640 --> 00:03:59,960
she must have screwed her over a lot.

59
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:03,160
I was definitely right to teach her a lesson today.

60
00:04:04,440 --> 00:04:05,720
I don't know if this Lu Jingheng

61
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:07,400
even understands the situation at all.

62
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,440
Telling me to reflect on myself.

63
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:09,480
Is he crazy?

64
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:11,640
Who is sick?

65
00:04:15,040 --> 00:04:16,160
Why are you here?

66
00:04:17,079 --> 00:04:18,040
Let me go.

67
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:47,420
Didn't you apply the medicine today?

68
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,400
Everyone in the Lu family hates me.

69
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:51,000
Who knows if it's poisonous?

70
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:54,240
I'm not that bored.

71
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:00,640
Give me your hand.

72
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:12,440
I'll do it myself.

73
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:14,720
Don't move.

74
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:46,240
Young Master.

75
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:57,560
Young Madam,

76
00:05:57,640 --> 00:05:59,200
I heard from the auntie downstairs

77
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:00,240
that after you left,

78
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:02,000
the Young Master kept speaking up for you

79
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,640
and venting your anger for you.

80
00:06:03,640 --> 00:06:04,440
Really?

81
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:05,880
Of course it's true.

82
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:08,240
The Young Master is actually quite nice,

83
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,800
just a bit cold usually.

84
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,720
Before, when the Su family bullied you,

85
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:12,840
whenever he knew about it,

86
00:06:12,840 --> 00:06:14,240
he would definitely stand up for you

87
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:15,570
to make you feel better.

88
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,480
In that case,

89
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:19,400
Lu Jingheng isn't the one who killed the original host.

90
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:20,560
He can be ruled out.

91
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,280
But Young Madam,

92
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:25,490
you shouldn't go against the Madam in the future.

93
00:06:25,520 --> 00:06:27,840
She and the cousin are both from the Su family.

94
00:06:27,840 --> 00:06:29,280
If you offend the cousin,

95
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:31,180
aren't you offending her too?

96
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:34,050
The Madam has punished you several times before.

97
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:35,360
Su Manyun.

98
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:39,300
Could the original host's death have something to do with her?

99
00:06:40,440 --> 00:06:42,400
Lili, thank you.

100
00:06:45,960 --> 00:06:46,760
Young Madam,

101
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,400
the Madam just said

102
00:06:48,440 --> 00:06:49,800
to have you prepare,

103
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:51,240
we have guests to entertain tomorrow.

104
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,240
Entertain how?

105
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:54,400
The Madam will entertain distinguished guests tomorrow.

106
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:55,720
She specifically ordered

107
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:58,050
that you wait on them on the side tomorrow.

108
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:00,120
Wait on them?

109
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:03,440
Just like before.

110
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:06,860
You stand next to the guests, pouring tea and water.

111
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:09,280
You can't sit until they leave.

112
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:11,880
Every time you have to stand for hours.

113
00:07:12,320 --> 00:07:13,560
Every time you finish serving,

114
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:15,360
you're left with an aching back.

115
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:19,000
A show of strength?

116
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,760
Let's see if I take it.

117
00:07:22,200 --> 00:07:23,960
Wh- What does that mean?

118
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,680
Your dress looks really nice.

119
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:32,159
Yours is not bad either.

120
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:34,120
Have you been busy lately?

121
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:34,880
Not too bad.

122
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:36,520
Today,

123
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:37,560
I asked you all to come over

124
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,920
mainly to catch up,

125
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:40,520
since it's been a while.

126
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:41,680
Secondly,

127
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:43,940
our Lu family has a new daughter-in-law.

128
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:46,480
Jingheng's wife.

129
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,560
Didn't you know?

130
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:49,560
That girl

131
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,960
is usually quite well-behaved,

132
00:07:50,960 --> 00:07:53,020
introverted, and doesn't talk much.

133
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:54,960
I thought I'd invite everyone

134
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:56,360
to let her see the world.

135
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:59,360
Young people should meet more people.

136
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:01,680
Mrs. Lu, you are very thoughtful.

137
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:08,200
Shen Zhixia.

138
00:08:08,520 --> 00:08:10,560
If Auntie doesn't teach you a lesson today,

139
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:11,920
I'm afraid you will forget

140
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:14,520
who the real master of the Lu family is.

141
00:08:15,520 --> 00:08:17,240
It must have cost a few million to decorate.

142
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,400
And Xiaoyu.

143
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:20,920
It looks good.

144
00:08:21,440 --> 00:08:22,770
Hurry up and draw a tile.

145
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:24,800
These tiles today are really...

146
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:27,560
What tile is this?

147
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,200
Come on.

148
00:08:28,960 --> 00:08:29,760
Red Dragon.

149
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:30,680
What terrible luck.

150
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:31,880
What are these tiles?

151
00:08:32,039 --> 00:08:32,840
White Dragon.

152
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:34,320
Pass.

153
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:35,640
Six of Dots.

154
00:08:36,159 --> 00:08:37,159
Six of Dots.

155
00:08:37,760 --> 00:08:39,679
Mahjong! Pay up.

156
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:40,880
You won again?

157
00:08:40,880 --> 00:08:42,080
How did you win again?

158
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:43,280
Pay up.

159
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:44,440
You're so good at this.

160
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:44,800
What amazing luck.

161
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:45,440
Teach us.

162
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,320
You're amazing.

163
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,560
Let me tell you.

164
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:50,360
No one leaves today until you learn.

165
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:52,400
From now on, when you play, you're all my apprentices.

166
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:52,960
Okay.

167
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:53,760
No problem.

168
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:56,960
Stepmom.

169
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:58,560
Stepmom is back.

170
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:01,160
Mrs. Lu.

171
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:03,320
Everyone has started playing.

172
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,480
Yes, that's right.

173
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:06,840
Stepmom,

174
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:07,600
there's no more hot water here.

175
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,860
Hurry up and boil some.

176
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:11,960
I remember my sister likes drinking tea the most, right?

177
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:12,760
Yes.

178
00:09:12,920 --> 00:09:14,040
Let me tell you,

179
00:09:14,040 --> 00:09:17,560
this black tea must be brewed with boiling water

180
00:09:17,640 --> 00:09:19,280
to bring out its aroma.

181
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:22,280
Yes, that's true.

182
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,760
Cousin Yuran.

183
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,120
Why are you standing so far back?

184
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,040
I didn't even notice you.

185
00:09:27,040 --> 00:09:28,320
Come closer.

186
00:09:28,560 --> 00:09:29,920
Come on.

187
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:32,880
This is my prettiest cousin.

188
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:33,960
She's a great beauty.

189
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:35,080
Indeed, a great beauty.

190
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,240
Mrs. Lin, let me tell you.

191
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,680
My cousin is just like you.

192
00:09:37,680 --> 00:09:39,920
She knows a lot about pastries.

193
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,680
I remember you like

194
00:09:41,680 --> 00:09:43,320
Liao's, right?

195
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,520
Do we have any at home?

196
00:09:44,760 --> 00:09:46,290
Let's get some for Mrs. Lin.

197
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:47,160
If not,

198
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,880
go out and buy some.

199
00:09:52,880 --> 00:09:54,960
I couldn't possibly ask your cousin to run an errand.

200
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:57,020
If you don't have any, just forget it.

201
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,680
My stepmother told me

202
00:09:58,680 --> 00:09:59,360
that we must serve our guests

203
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:01,720
warmly and thoughtfully.

204
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:02,850
Right, Stepmother?

205
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:05,960
Yes, yes, yes, that's what I said.

206
00:10:07,280 --> 00:10:08,080
Mrs. Wang.

207
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,720
Come and play a few rounds for me.

208
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:10,480
Come, come, come.

209
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:11,400
My back is sore.

210
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:13,410
I haven't played in a while.

211
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:15,200
Collect the money.

212
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:16,040
Stepmother,

213
00:10:18,280 --> 00:10:20,120
the kitchen is over there.

214
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,120
Sister.

215
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:25,960
Pastries.

216
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,520
Mrs. Lu,

217
00:10:29,520 --> 00:10:31,480
you are so virtuous,

218
00:10:31,680 --> 00:10:33,960
helping our young madam

219
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:35,920
with the chores.

220
00:10:35,920 --> 00:10:37,960
My stepmother is the best.

221
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:41,760
Stepmother.

222
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:43,650
My stepmother just said

223
00:10:43,680 --> 00:10:46,000
she will cover all your losses.

224
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:46,800
Let's say,

225
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:49,000
Thank you, stepmother.

226
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:50,600
Thank you, Mrs. Lu.

227
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:51,720
Mrs. Lu is so generous.

228
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:53,960
As long as you're having fun.

229
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:56,520
Put it all on my tab.

230
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:01,120
Stepmom is so nice.

231
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:02,560
Keep playing.

232
00:11:02,560 --> 00:11:03,040
Come on.

233
00:11:03,040 --> 00:11:04,560
Come play again next time.

234
00:11:04,560 --> 00:11:05,560
Come on, let's continue.

235
00:11:05,560 --> 00:11:06,320
Let's play another round.

236
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,600
Let's play a round.

237
00:11:09,680 --> 00:11:11,120
A show of strength?

238
00:11:11,160 --> 00:11:13,020
It depends on whether I accept it.

239
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:14,640
What?

240
00:11:14,640 --> 00:11:15,120
What 'Wei'?

241
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:17,720
I said increase the power for the next round.

242
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:20,720
Come on, let's play.

